1) use natural language to scan social media for negativity.
2) try classify to see if it is overwhelming and maybe “emotional”
3) estimate intrinsic value, if  it is more than current value hen pursue.
4) use different prediction methods and scales to see how much further down it might go.
5) micro invest
6) use predictions methods again but to forecast when/if it recovers and predict when to sell.
7) watch social media for when positive news starts appearing then sell

